Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:38.57,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}LYLA...初めて息をした
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.16,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\yshad2}想要知道什么  一秒就有答案
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.20,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\yshad2}在这便利至上的时代
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.46,ED_CH,,700,0,0,,{\yshad2}满屏的广告与恶意  一指便能轻松解决
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.21,ED_CH,,1000,0,0,,{\yshad2}可在你面前  我却乱了节奏
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.01,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\yshad2}变得像疯掉的人偶一般
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.47,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\yshad2}你还真是神奇
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.47,0:22:51.43,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\yshad2}我的伪装如春雪融化般渐渐褪去
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.43,0:22:57.11,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\yshad2}伴随倾心爱慕而生
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.53,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\yshad2}这份酸甜与苦涩让我束手无策
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.36,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\yshad2}想逃离现代生活
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.49,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\yshad2}将一切都毁掉吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.49,0:23:10.83,ED_CH,,0,700,0,,{\yshad2}侵蚀心底的病毒  根本找不到解法
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.83,0:23:13.12,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}疼痛啊  疼痛啊  都飞走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.46,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}1.2.3  敲击漏电
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.46,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}麻痹刺痛  不停震颤
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.42,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\yshad2}想逃离现代生活
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.68,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\yshad2}每次触碰都改变的算法
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.68,0:23:28.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}将「那是拟人化」的诡辩揉成纸团丢掉  来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.85,0:23:30.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}别按下UNDO
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.44,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}哪怕这是本世纪最大错误
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.44,0:23:38.57,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\yshad2}LYLA...第一次呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.16,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想要知道什么  一秒就有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.20,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}在这便利至上的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.46,ED_CH,,700,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}满屏的广告与恶意  一指便能轻松解决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.21,ED_CH,,1000,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}可在你面前  我却乱了节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.01,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}变得像疯掉的人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.47,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}你还真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:51.43,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}我的伪装如春雪融化般渐渐褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:57.11,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}伴随倾心爱慕而生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.53,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}这份酸甜与苦涩让我束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.36,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃离现代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.49,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}将一切都毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:10.83,ED_CH,,0,700,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}侵蚀心底的病毒  根本找不到解法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:13.12,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}疼痛啊  疼痛啊  都飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.46,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}1.2.3  敲击漏电
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.46,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}麻痹刺痛  不停震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.42,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃离现代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.68,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}每次触碰都改变的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:28.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}将「那是拟人化」的诡辩揉成纸团丢掉  来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:30.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}别按下UNDO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.44,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}哪怕这是本世纪最大错误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:38.57,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}LYLA...第一次呼吸
